title: East Catholic triumphs
text:
East Catholic triumphs By Journal Inquirer Staff Journal Inquirer | 0 comments 
East Catholic 95, E.O. Smith 86 
Kelly Chmielewski won the 100 freestyle and 100 backstroke and Samantha Dickinson, Shannon Leary and Gabby Caron added a win apiece to lead East Catholic to a convincing win over E.O. Smith.
